<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>JESUS BIDS UN SHINE</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Isu'n ei vak sak, vak thiengtho takin,
 Zana thaumeivak neu a vak tawbangin;
 Zie thimna khawvel ahin vak hitiu,
 Nang na umna mun ah, kei ka mun ah.

[V2]
 2. Isu'n ei vaksak Amah a dingin,
 Chien takin A mui I vak hawih leh hawih loh;
 Van apatin A en I vak mu di'n,
 Nang na umna mun ah, kei ka mun ah.

[V3]
 3. Isu'n ei vak sak mi dangte a di'n,
 Thimna chitin in khawvel hi a tuomvel;
 Gitloh, lungkhamna lakah vak hitiu,
 Nang na umna mun ah, kei ka mun ah.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>451</hymn_number>
</song>